:

1. *Drugu* nedelju razgovaramo o nauci. (We talk about science the next week.)
2. Kada je *drugu* sestru rodio njegov otac? (When did his father give birth to his second sister?)
3. Predstavnici *drugu* stranu su odbili. (The representatives of the other side refused.)
4. Ona je prošla *drugu* godinu studija. (She passed the second year of studies.)
5. Kupio je *drugu* kucu. (He bought a second house.)
6. Znam da je ona otišla u *drugu* zemlju. (I know that she went to another country.)
7. On je izabrao *drugu* stranu. (He chose the other side.)
8. On je napravio *drugu* grešku. (He made a second mistake.)